China 's Highest TV Drama Awards
ZHENGZHOU , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- China 's annual Feitian Awards , its top awards for television dramas , were announced here today .
" Outlaws of the Marsh " , the screen version of a classic novel of the same title , won the TV Drama of the Year award .
Critics say it brought TV productions of dramas based on classical literature to a new high .
TV works based on other classical novels like " A Dream of Red Mansions " , " A Journey to the West " , and " The Three Kingdoms Romance " have appeared on the screen a number of times .
There were 166 TV dramas competing for this year 's awards .
